articles.title: New COVID Variant XEC Is Spreading in Europe. Here's What You Need to Know - Verywell Health
articles.description: Experts say the variant might become dominant globally in the next few months.
articles.content:
• The new COVID-19 variant XEC is spreading quickly in Europe and may soon become the dominant variant worldwide.
  • XEC is a recombinant variant made up of two JN.1-related strains.
